  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are trapped in a memory of your past. Observe your surrounding carefully to end your nightmare. Keep an eye out for anomalies to advance your day, or get trapped in an endless loop. Estimated play time 30 minutes to 2 hours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Home_0 is a phycological horror where you play as 9-year-old boy relieving his memories on the most horrifying week.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Help yourself to get rid of the anomalies in your memories by choosing the right choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/364d2a69c3977913d9a45f10013324a3.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/364d2a69c3977913d9a45f10013324a3.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9305fdb36fe57d7094180aad89be5a51.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9305fdb36fe57d7094180aad89be5a51.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9305fdb36fe57d7094180aad89be5a51.mp4?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RULE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rule of the game is simple:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you find anomalies, exit from your house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't find any anomalies, go to sleep</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/4ec4a156bc57741f627632d38a34a0fb.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/4ec4a156bc57741f627632d38a34a0fb.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9d0c50d3c39bafcf4597fafd126e9700.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9d0c50d3c39bafcf4597fafd126e9700.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/9d0c50d3c39bafcf4597fafd126e9700.mp4?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose correctly to progress a day. Get it wrong and you will restart from day 1. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to day 10 to reach the conclusion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/da40116df383e57bd452ad39a221b66f.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/da40116df383e57bd452ad39a221b66f.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/a49d9f5835202f61c7d50025dc780e33.poster.avif?t=1746457520\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/a49d9f5835202f61c7d50025dc780e33.webm?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066510/extras/a49d9f5835202f61c7d50025dc780e33.mp4?t=1746457520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS style retro graphic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story-Rich</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Endings</p></li></ul>",
